Source: flowcanvas
Priority: extra
Maintainer: Dave Robillard <dave@drobilla.net>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 5), autotools-dev
Standards-Version: 3.7.3
Section: libs

Package: flowcanvas
Depends: flowcanvas-0
Architecture: any
Description: An interactive graph canvas widget in C++ (Gtkmm)
 FlowCanvas is an interactive Gtkmm/Gnomecanvasmm widget for graph-based
 interfaces (patchers, modular synthesizers, finite state automata,
 interactive graphs, etc).

Package: flowcanvas-dev
Depends: flowcanvas-0-dev
Architecture: any
Description: Development files (headers) for FlowCanvas
 Files required for compiling programs which use FlowCanvas.

