Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, libgnomecanvasmm-2.6-1c2a
Description: An interactive graph canvas widget in C++ (Gtkmm)
 FlowCanvas is an interactive Gtkmm/Gnomecanvasmm widget for graph-based
 interfaces (patchers, modular synthesizers, finite state automata,
 interactive graphs, etc).

Package: flowcanvas-0-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
